            <title>[THRIFT-2911] fix c++ version zeromq transport, the old version cannot work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/THRIFT-2911</link>
                <project id="12310800" key="THRIFT">Thrift</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;GitHub user littletiny opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/315&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/315&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    fix c++ version zeromq transport, the old version cannot work&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    fix c++ version zeromq transport, the old version cannot work&lt;br/&gt;
    we need to override&lt;br/&gt;
    ```&lt;br/&gt;
     TTransport::write_virt  TTransport::read_virt&lt;br/&gt;
    ```&lt;br/&gt;
    instead of&lt;br/&gt;
    ```&lt;br/&gt;
     TTransport::write TTransport::read&lt;br/&gt;
    ```&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;You can merge this pull request into a Git repository by running:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    $ git pull &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/littletiny/thrift&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/littletiny/thrift&lt;/a&gt; master&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Alternatively you can review and apply these changes as the patch at:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/315.patch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/thrift/pull/315.patch&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

